data.description: Charming  2 bedroom 1 bath home in Eden Pines; a wonderful family neighborhood located in Big Pine Key where the Key Deer roam in their National Refuge. Dead end street makes it extra safe for kids with no through traffic. With a fenced yard, this home is a great fit for families with children and dogs, providing a safe space for both to enjoy.The house is on short stilts, a few steps inside and just enough so it's not on the direct ground as it has never flooded! Brand new split unit AC in the main living area keeps the home cool, the bedrooms each have a mini split which is excellent for energy efficiency.  Butcher block countertops, farm sink, interior laundry room, metal roof, glass top range & elevated water heater.The Keys is all about the water! The boat ramp is conveniently within walking distance to launch for a great day at the reef, fishing or to the sandbar. Your own piece of paradise awaits!
